<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Week 8 Room 5 Humanities</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0b0c10;
            --card-bg: #1f2833;
            --panel-inner: #0f141c;
            --text-main: #ffffff;
            --text-muted: #c5a059;
            --border-color: #45a29e;
            --accent-gold: #ffb830;
            --accent-g1: #ff5252;
            --accent-g2: #ff793f;
            --accent-g3: #33d9b2;
            --accent-g4: #34ace0;
            --accent-g5: #a29bfe;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif; }
        body { background-color: var(--bg-color); color: var(--text-main); min-height: 100vh; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
        
        header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #12161f, #1f2833); padding: 15px 25px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 4px solid var(--accent-gold); }
        header h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #fff; }
        header p { color: #66fcf1; font-size: 0.95rem; margin-top: 4px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 1px; }

        .day-selector { display: flex; justify-content: center; background-color: #0c0f14; padding: 10px; gap: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #2a3545; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .day-btn { background-color: #151b24; color: white; border: 2px solid transparent; padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.88rem; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .day-btn.active { background-color: var(--accent-gold); color: #000; border-color: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 184, 48, 0.4); }

        .tabs { display: flex; justify-content: center; background-color: #121720; padding: 8px 0; gap: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #2a3545; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .tabs .tab-btn { background-color: #1c2331; color: #a2aab8; border: 2px solid transparent; padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; }
        .tabs .tab-btn[data-group="1"].active { border-color: var(--accent-g1); color: var(--accent-g1); background: rgba(255,82,82,0.15); }
        .tabs .tab-btn[data-group="2"].active { border-color: var(--accent-g2); color: var(--accent-g2); background: rgba(255,121,63,0.15); }
        .tabs .tab-btn[data-group="3"].active { border-color: var(--accent-g3); color: var(--accent-g3); background: rgba(51,217,178,0.15); }
        .tabs .tab-btn[data-group="4"].active { border-color: var(--accent-g4); color: var(--accent-g4); background: rgba(52,172,224,0.15); }
        .tabs .tab-btn[data-group="5"].active { border-color: var(--accent-g5); color: var(--accent-g5); background: rgba(162,155,254,0.15); }

        .main-container { flex: 1; display: flex; gap: 15px; padding: 15px; max-width: 1600px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; }
        .workspace { flex: 2.2; background-color: var(--card-bg); border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; border-left: 10px solid transparent; transition: border-color 0.2s; overflow-y: auto; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
        
        .slide-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; border-bottom: 2px solid #2a3545; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; }
        .slide-header h2 { font-size: 1.35rem; color: #fff; }
        .roster-tag { font-size: 0.85rem; background-color: #0c0f14; padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 4px; color: #cbd2e1; border: 1px solid #2a3545; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: bold; }
        
        .audio-controls { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; background: #121720; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #2a3545; }
        .audio-btn { border: none; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; font-size: 0.82rem; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
        .audio-btn:hover { opacity: 0.9; }
        .audio-btn.play { background-color: #2e86de; color: white; }
        .audio-btn.stop { background-color: #ee5253; color: white; }

        .waltham { background: #0f141c; padding: 14px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 15px; border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-gold); line-height: 1.45; }
        
        .custom-text-panel { background: #1a222d; border: 1px solid #34495e; padding: 18px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #eaeff5; font-size: 0.98rem; max-height: 280px; overflow-y: auto; box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
        .custom-text-panel h4 { color: var(--accent-gold); margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 1.1rem; border-bottom: 1px dashed #34495e; padding-bottom: 4px; }

        .word-span { display: inline-block; padding: 0 2px; margin-right: 2px; border-radius: 3px; transition: all 0.1s ease; color: #eaeff5; }
        .word-span.highlight { background-color: #ffb830 !important; color: #000000 !important; font-weight: bold; box-shadow: 0 0 8px #ffb830; transform: scale(1.05); }

        .panel { background-color: var(--panel-inner); border: 1px solid #2a3545; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .panel h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 12px; padding-bottom: 5px; border-bottom: 1px solid #2a3545; color: var(--accent-gold); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
        .panel li { margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.5; color: #e1e4ed; list-style-position: inside; }
        
        .links-box { background: rgba(52, 172, 224, 0.1); border: 1px dashed var(--accent-g4); padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.9rem; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px; align-items: center; }
        .links-box a { color: #71c1ff; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; padding: 4px 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid rgba(113, 193, 255, 0.2); transition: all 0.2s; }
        .links-box a:hover { background: rgba(113, 193, 255, 0.2); transform: translateY(-1px); }

        .sidebar { flex: 1.1; background-color: var(--card-bg); border-radius: 8px; padding: 18px; border-top: 5px solid var(--accent-gold); display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
        .sidebar h2 { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #fff; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 2px solid #2a3545; padding-bottom: 6px; text-align: center; }
        
        .book-mockup { background-color: #fffdf5; border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08), 3px 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.25); padding: 15px 15px; color: #222; position: relative; border-left: 6px solid #e67e22; flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 290px; max-height: 350px; }
        .book-mockup .margin-line { position: absolute; left: 25px; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 1px; background-color: #ff7675; }
        .book-mockup .notebook-line { border-bottom: 1px solid #b2bec3; height: 26px; line-height: 26px; font-size: 0.75rem; padding-left: 15px; position: relative; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; }
        
        .book-mockup .date-text { color: #2d3436; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; border-bottom: 2px solid #ff4d4d; padding-bottom: 1px; line-height: 1.1; }
        .book-mockup .title-text { font-weight: bold; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #2d3436; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.78rem; padding-bottom: 1px; }
        .book-mockup .question-text { color: #2d3436; font-weight: 500; }
        .book-mockup .answer-prompt { color: #0984e3; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.70rem; }
        .book-mockup .drawing-container { border: 1px dashed #636e72; background: #fff; height: 42px; width: 110px; margin: 6px 0 2px 15px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.65rem; color: #636e72; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; border-radius: 4px; align-self: flex-start; }

        footer { text-align: center; padding: 10px; background-color: #0c0f14; font-size: 0.75rem; color: #62687f; border-top: 1px solid #2a3545; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Week 8 Room 5 Humanities</h1>
        <p>INDEPENDENT READING COMPREHENSION</p>
